      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just corruption though. i checked the server logs like u said and there's no record of any login attempts or deletions from that period. it's like the data was just... erased from the actual side of things. and i noticed it's only stuff from that specific year when i was working on that tech project. it feels way too targeted to be a random hacker. do these big companies ever do stuff like this to people?",
